                        <span class="g-bg-black-opacity-0_6 g-px-5">e scoprite chi sono...</span>
                    </h3>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-8">
                    <img class="img-responsive" src="~/Assets/img/home/1.jpg" alt="">
                   
